  "texts": [
    "Moreover, OpenFedLLM is open-source 1, making it accessible to the broader research community and fostering collaboration in the development of federated language models.",
    "• Pretrained Models for Multilingual Federated Learning: This study addresses the complex challenges of utilizing pretrained language models within a federated learning context across multiple languages.",
    "Weller et al. 's work is crucial for understanding how multilingualism impacts federated learning algorithms, particularly exploring the effects of non-IID (independently and identically distributed) data inherent in natural language processing tasks across different languages.",
